OL,7,FScotland's First Minister has said
OL,8,Fhis mother-in-law, who is stuck in
OL,9,FGaza, has "lost hope".
OL,11,FElizabeth El-Nakla and her husband
OL,12,FMaged travelled to the region before
OL,13,Fthe Hamas attack but they have been
OL,14,Fleft trapped by Israel's retaliation.
OL,16,FHolding back tears, Humza Yousaf
OL,17,Freiterated calls for a ceasefire, an
OL,18,Fincrease in aid and a global refugee
OL,19,Fsettlement scheme to be created for
OL,20,Fthose who wish to flee.
OL,3,C'She's lost hope': Humza Yousaf holds
OL,4,Cback tears in emotional update on
OL,5,Cmother-in-law stuck in Gaza
